# .clinerules — Voxtral Pod
# Règles de contexte pour LLM (Qwen 3 3B, Mistral Small, etc.)
# Lire ce fichier EN PREMIER avant toute modification.
- no side effects
- pure functions only
- full typing required
- must pass ruff
- must pass mypy strict

## STACK TECHNIQUE
- Backend  : Python 3.11+, FastAPI, SQLite (jobs.db), asyncio
- Frontend : HTML/CSS (DSFR), Vanilla JS (app.js), WebSocket
- ASR      : faster-whisper (local GPU), Albert API (distant, no GPU)
- Audio    : ffmpeg obligatoire, webrtcvad + silero_vad (VAD)
- Tests    : pytest, variable env TESTING=1 active le mode mock

## STRUCTURE DES FICHIERS (ne pas déplacer)
```
backend/
  main.py          # Point d'entrée FastAPI + lifespan
  config.py        # Constantes, chemins, setup GPU/warnings
  state.py         # SQLite CRUD (jobs, config, asr_engine singleton)
  utils.py         # format_transcription() → HTML
  cleanup.py       # Nettoyage fichiers/jobs (tâche async périodique)
  html_ui.py       # Template HTML inline (HTML_UI constant)
  cli_tools.py     # CLI keyring
  routes/
    api.py         # Tous les endpoints HTTP + WebSocket /live
  core/
    engine.py      # SotaASR : orchestrateur principal
    transcription.py # TranscriptionEngine (whisper/vosk/albert/mock)
    diarization.py   # DiarizationEngine (pyannote, GPU)
    diarization_cpu.py # LightDiarizationEngine (CPU stub)
    audio.py       # decode_audio(), pcm_to_float32(), float32_to_pcm16()
    vad.py         # VADManager (webrtcvad + silero, dual-gate)
    live.py        # LiveSession (WebSocket par connexion)
    merger.py      # assign_speakers_to_words(), smooth_micro_turns(), build_speaker_segments()
    postprocess.py # _call_albert(), summarize_text(), clean_text(), extract_actions_text()
    assistant.py   # AlbertAssistant (wrapper async postprocess)
    speaker_profiles.py # SQLite profils voix (resemblyzer embeddings)
static/
  app.js           # Frontend JS (WebSocket, batch upload, historique)
  index.html       # HTML statique (servi si pas de template inline)
  postprocess.js   # JS page résultat post-traitement
